# Defensive deny-list — belt-and-suspenders.
# This chezmoi source only tracks an explicit allowlist, but never let any of
# the following be committed even if added by mistake or by tooling.

# --- Sensitive application data directories ---
Signal/
chromium/
chrome/
pulse/
ibus/
dconf/
systemd/
fcitx*/

# --- Credentials / browser state / databases ---
Cookies*
Login Data*
Web Data*
Local State
History
*.sqlite
*.sqlite-*
*.ldb

# --- Caches and volatile state ---
*Cache*
logs/
*.log

# --- Editor / migration backups ---
*.bak
*.bak.*
